{"word":"G4573 - σεβάζομαι - sebázomai - seb-ad'-zom-ahee - Worship","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σεβάζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sebázomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">seb-ad'-zom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Worship</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தொழு"},{"paragraph":"1. to fear, be afraid"},{"paragraph":"2. to honor religiously, to worship"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Middle voice from a derivative of <a href=\"#/G4576 - σέβομαι - sébomai - seb'-om-ahee/4576\">G4576</a>; to <i>venerate</i>, that is, <i>adore:</i> - worship.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2150/2150\">G2150</a>, <a href=\"#/G2151/2151\">G2151</a>, <a href=\"#/G2152/2152\">G2152</a>, <a href=\"#/G2153/2153\">G2153</a>, <a href=\"#/G4573/4573\">G4573</a>, <a href=\"#/G4574/4574\">G4574</a>, <a href=\"#/G4575/4575\">G4575</a>, <a href=\"#/G4576/4576\">G4576</a>, <a href=\"#/G763/763\">G763</a>, <a href=\"#/G764/764\">G764</a>, <a href=\"#/G765/765\">G765</a>"}]}